edu.ucla.sspace.evaluation

Interface WordChoiceReport


  • public interface WordChoiceReport
    A report of the performance of a SemanticSpace on a particular WordChoiceEvaluation test.
    Author:
    David Jurgens

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      int correctAnswers()
      Returns the number of questions that were answered correctly.
      int numberOfQuestions()
      Returns the total number of questions on the test.
      double score()
      Returns the score, ranged between 0 and 100, achieved on a particlar evaluation.
      int unanswerableQuestions()
      Returns the number of questions for which the SemanticSpace could not give an answer due to missing word vectors in either the prompt or the options.
